{"tid":2120873,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"戰狼外交失敗 中共陷孤立","createTime":"2020-07-23T03:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T04:08:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"df8ca087df897a6ba7cb13d3fa0f61df61ad75f6","tid":2120873,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T03:17:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200723/JUT4VWPSA7OCWO5GYIW7ZU2SNM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200723%2FJUT4VWPSA7OCWO5GYIW7ZU2SNM%2F&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgEn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=c7ea501a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200723%2FJUT4VWPSA7OCWO5GYIW7ZU2SNM%2F&h=dbb9d90f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200723/JUT4VWPSA7OCWO5GYIW7ZU2SNM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n戰狼外交失敗 中共陷孤立<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美國國務卿蓬佩奧訪問英國、丹麥之際，美國國務院大開逐客令，勒令中國駐侯斯頓總領事館關閉，反映中國國家主席習近平「戰狼外交」大挫敗。專家表示，中美陷入全面冷戰，估計美方將在香港問題上「加辣」，不排除制裁包括國務院港澳辦主任夏寶龍等中共非政治局官員。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。作為中國資深外交家，崔天凱向央視名嘴白岩松洩露「天機」，就是中美目前「無偈傾」，關係異常：「現在連對話都沒有，應該說是很不正常的情況。」。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2q6HKWq37sji5-j3vdBvDGDbOqg=/1106x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LCIP4QDU2KPHZPF45ERTBRPAC4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2q6HKWq37sji5-j3vdBvDGDbOqg%3D%2F1106x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLCIP4QDU2KPHZPF45ERTBRPAC4.jpg&h=3183b83a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n崔天凱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n專家：中美關係難有轉機<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：中共訂明四招銷毀密件<br />\n<br />\n崔天凱。。。。。。。。。。。。。其實，蓬佩奧看來還有第二招，他將於美國西岸時間23日星期四下午1時40分（<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">香港時間周五清晨4時40分）在加州尼克遜總統圖書館，就共產中國和自由世界的未來議題發表演說，蓬佩奧會否再下一城，宣告美國對華政策大轉變，外界高度關注。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。林和立指出，美國勒令中國駐侯斯頓總領事館關閉，反映中美陷入全面冷戰，兩國關係進一步倒退，預期今年11月美國大選前中美關係亦難有轉機。<br />\n<br />\n林和立指出，習近平上台以來推出戰狼外交、亮劍外交，大力發展航空母艦等先進武器，引起歐美等國的猜疑，令中國陷入40年來的孤立境地。他指出，習近平戰狼外交乏善足陳，雷聲大雨點小，一帶一路幾近銷聲匿迹。今年武漢肺炎大流行再加上香港問題，令中國在全球外交幾陷孤立，澳洲、日本一致針對中國，中國「老朋友」俄羅斯總統普京鮮有在外為習說一兩句好話，習外交思路、政策以及舉措均告失敗。"},{"pid":"c6867728c83df1439c9fe9c8540ef527e554d302","tid":2120873,"uid":46356,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T03:19:50.000Z","msg":"但起碼真係做到令德國夾住歐盟唔敢孤立老共囉"},{"pid":"d1d47bd101e139a1a4529a532658a6cec6a451ab","tid":2120873,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T03:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec8c4ded8be077507e670ebe52a08da4984b05a","tid":2120873,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T03:23:31.000Z","msg":"每條選擇題，題題都答錯晒，無條撞得岩，都係一種高技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d20b7d366a909ccd1800b1684cc09692ee8e2b","tid":2120873,"uid":230594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T03:28:34.000Z","msg":"仲有一班等出糧嘅國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4adf23618647e6556a9144826f3a8854428c3004","tid":2120873,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T03:37:06.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5378aa3aad72037e46de46502b3edc9b0735060e","tid":2120873,"uid":73340,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T03:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jYShm9f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjYShm9f.gif&h=fd64f24f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁樣邊